Returns whether aBitVar matches the pattern "pattern". The pattern length is 1-64
                characters. Only the characters "0" and "1" are accepted, all others are ignored!
                For example the interpretation of the pattern strings: "1011x01" means, bit 2 is
                ignored, bit 0, 1, 3, 4, 5, 6 have to fit.
PatternComment0aBitVarmust contain 0 at the appropriate position1aBitVarmust contain 1 at the appropriate position
