This example uses aControl++class and an object of a Control++ class to output values that
                are set for specific datapoints via the PARA module. The scope lib of a panel
                contains the class DpCon and the work function that outputs the values set for
                specific datapoints via PARA. The datapoints are specified via dpConnect().
