  newShape.foreCol("{255,255,255}");
}
Example 4
The example is started in a script belonging to the object "Elipsis1" and retrieves a
                shape pointer to the object itself with an empty string parameter.
main()
{
  shape s;
  s = getShape("");
  DebugTN("expected: shapePtr --> returned: ", s);
}

