returnValue:
-1, 0 for GEDI.
Description
This CTRL function is used to set the dollar parameters of a reference. This function
                may only be used under Windows (GEDI, reference configuration panel). The reference
                configuration panel is opened by the script openRefParamPanel.ctl.
Example
Sets the dollar parameters of the graphics reference (by clicking onOKin the
                reference panel).
main()
{
  // Counter
  int lines, n;
  // Arguments for "setDollarParams()"
  string refName;
  dyn_string dollars;
  dyn_string values;
  // Gets the assigned name for the reference
  getValue("refNameBox", "text", refName);
  // Gets the assigned values for the reference
  getValue("tab", "lineCount", lines);
  for(n=1; n<=lines; n++)
  {
    getValue("tab", "cellValueRC", n-1, "dollarParams",
    dollars[n]);
    getValue("tab", "cellValueRC", n-1, "value", values[n]);
  }
  setDollarParams(refName, dollars, values);
  closeDialog();
}

